<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06051n"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06051n">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06051n"> 51(n)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Dobbin&apos;ll be<font color="green">[duing]</font></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Si L. refusait &eacute;nergiquement de faire une chose, sa m&egrave;re n&apos;avait qu&apos;&agrave; lui dire: <mark>&ldquo;Dobbin voudrait que tu le fasses,&rdquo;</mark> et il ob&eacute;issait sans murmurer.&rdquo; <font color="green">[If L. energetically refused to do anything, his mother had only to say to him: &ldquo;Dobbin would like you to do it,&rdquo; and he obeyed without murmuring.]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 92</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
